Package at.fhooe.mc.conconii

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Observer
    Customized observer pattern interface
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActualData
    This class is a simple data container class for storing the measurement points.
    BluetoothService
    This is the service for creating a ble connection and for receiving data from the GATT serve.
    DataManager
    The DataManager must be used to get data from any sensor.
    EvaluationActivity
    This Activity displays a human readable representation of data collected during the test.
    EvaluationCalculator
    This class is used to create a list of final data which can be used to display in EvaluationActivity.
    GpsService
    This is the service for receiving gps data which is sent to the DataManger This service runs in his own thread and listens for Location updates
    MainActivity
    The MainActivity displays two major layouts: the startscreen and the mainActivity layout.
    Observable
    Customized observer pattern class
    ScanActivity
    Activity for scanning and displaying available Bluetooth LE devices.
    ScanActivity.ViewHolder
    Class for holding the View.
    TutorialActivity
    This activity is for showing a short tutorial about the Conconii-Test.
